{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM04_ST3_730.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x2b,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "*sigh*<CR>The solar eclipse ended...<CR>This was an epic failure..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "It's impossible to find a specific flower in just a few minutes in such a vast place..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "That reminds me, I wonder how Ranun and Ernie did..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x19f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Greetings, Ayesha. I came to find you, since I calculated that you'd start to miss me right about now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Hm? So this is the cute apothecary's workshop... Simple, sturdy, and boorish... Very good."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "D-Don't say boorish!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x157,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Oh, I beg your pardon. By any account,<CR>I shouldn't have used such a word to<CR>describe a girl's abode."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x158,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "To apologize, I'll serenade you with this sweet tune of salt and sand that I created last night, and‐"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Oh, but I'd be even happier if you could tell me the story of the solar eclipse and the flower."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x159,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Oops, I almost forgot the purpose of my visit."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Of course. In fact, I came here today to recount that story to you through song."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Ah! Then, you found the flower...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x196,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Stop. The answer will be revealed through my storytelling."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x188,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Driven by the gods of the sun and moon, in pursuit of a miraculous encounter, I arrived at the erstwhile seaside."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x189,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "However, the god that smiled upon me was not of the sun or the moon..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x18b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "But it was the mischievous god, Loki.<CR>O god, this is beyond unreasonable. "
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x18d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "In pursuit of the flower, I slipped as I wandered around the cliff, and proceeded headlong to the bottom..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x18d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Having fallen down flat, I swooned, but when my consciousness returned, what I beheld was..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "*gulp* Wh-What did you see...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x18e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "The sun, the same as usual, as the solar eclipse had ended. The end."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc7,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Ugh. So you mean, you fell off a cliff and the solar eclipse came and went while you were knocked out...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Heeey, don't get too discouraged.<CR>You're gonna make me sad, as well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "If you would like, I'd love to share the story thereafter of the cute little lump on the back of my head‐"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, Ayesha, Ayesha!<CR>I have big news for you!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xca,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Kyah! I've never seen you this flustered... What happened?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x7a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Of course I'd be flustered,<CR>because I...I saw Nio!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Huh?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x7b,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "I know what I saw, it was Nio. On the day of the solar eclipse, in a field of glowing flowers, I definitely saw her."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x7b,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "She disappeared quickly, but Nio, she saw me and smiled."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x7b,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "It wasn't a ghost... It was just like you said, Ayesha!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "How whimsical...<CR>Are you sure about that, Ernie?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x7c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "Absolutely. I have proof, too. See, this is the flower that was blooming by her side."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "I like flowers, so I'm quite familiar with them, but I've never seen a flower like this before."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "It seemed like it was special, so I picked one up."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "Is that...the flower that doesn't bloom in the sun...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "Seems like your story was true. Oh, how cruel the god of song and poetry can be."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "What good would it do to show such a fantastic scene to a merchant and not a poet!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe6,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "If I were to have seen such a spectacle, I could've written a splendid song that would've gone on into perpetuity."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x5f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "Hmhm. Maybe that's because of your everyday behavior?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe8,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "Do you mean to say that my everyday conduct is bad? Heh, that's weird. I don't have the slightest idea how."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "B-But, because the three of us searched, I was able to find a clue about Nio."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "msg_string": "It's all thanks to the both of you. Thank you so much."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "You got Eclipse Petals."
        }
    ]
}